            "image_full_width": true,
            "retina": true,
            "title": "Feels Good for the Sole",
            "text": "<p>Since 2012, we’ve been designing shoes that don’t follow the crowd—because neither do you. Every design starts with original art inked by independent artists, inspired by nature around the world, crafted with bold colors and details you won’t find anywhere else. </p>",
