            "retina": true,
            "title": "Ethically Handcrafted",
            "text": "<p>We don’t just design shoes. We build experiences—for your feet and your soul. With artful designs and premium materials that are cushioned, lightweight, and mold to your movement, our shoes are made to move with you wherever the day takes you.</p>",
